* feat: 添加新的日志库和相关文件，更新项目配置
* style: 重构MainWindow.h，移除多余的空行和空格
* Add UI dialogs for chat, login, registration, and password reset
- Implement ChatDialog for chat interface. - Create LoginDialog with user authentication features and UI enhancements. - Develop RegisterDialog for user registration, including email verification. - Introduce ResetDialog for password reset functionality with email verification. - Enhance UI elements with custom styles and animations for better user experience. - Integrate HTTP request handling for user actions across all dialogs.
* feat: 添加 GlitchTextWidget 组件及其实现，更新 Sidebar 和 CustomChatWindow 以支持新组件
* feat: 添加 GlitchTextWidget 组件，更新 Sidebar 和 CustomChatWindow 以支持新功能
* Add custom chat window SVG icon
* feat: 更新项目配置，添加新的 UI 组件和图标资源
* feat: 更新 Sidebar 和 CustomSidebar 以支持可扩展宽度，添加动画效果
* Add Gradient Knob and Point Wave Animation components
- Introduced `KnobPage` and `TemperatureDial` classes for a gradient knob UI component. - Implemented animation functionality using `TimerAnimation` for smooth transitions in the knob. - Added `PointWaveAnimation` class to create a dynamic wave effect with dots. - Updated `CustomChatWindow` to integrate `PointWaveAnimation` for enhanced visual feedback. - Refactored existing sidebar and utility classes to accommodate new animation features.
* feat: 更新 CustomChatWindow 和 CustomSidebar 以支持新功能
* feat: 更新 CustomChatWindow 和 CustomSidebar 以支持新功能
* Refactor Sidebar and MainWindow components
- Fixed typo in Sidebar.h comment for addWidget method. - Cleaned up Sidebar.cpp by removing commented-out animation code in expand and shrink methods. - Updated resizeEvent in Sidebar.cpp to remove unnecessary comments. - Adjusted spacing in MainWindow.h for consistency. - Commented out the call to initializeFaceDetectUI in MainWindow.cpp for future implementation.
* feat: 添加 GenerateLineAnimation 组件并在 CustomChatWindow 中集成
* refactor: 清理 Sidebar 和 CustomChatWindow 组件代码
* Add RoundMenuMainWindow implementation for circular rotating menu demo
- Introduced a new class `RoundMenuMainWindow` to demonstrate the functionality of the `RoundMenuWidget`. - Implemented UI setup with controls for adding, removing, and clearing menu items. - Added color customization options for the center button, menu items, and hover effects. - Included options for displaying background, separator lines, and enabling rotation animations. - Integrated presets for different menu styles: classic, cool, and minimalist. - Connected signals and slots for interactive behavior of the menu and controls. - Set up demo menu items with icons and tooltips for user interaction.
* feat: Implement ContactCardWidget with expandable contact methods and animations
- Created ContactCardWidget class to display user contact information. - Added functionality for expandable/collapsible contact methods with animations. - Implemented methods to set user name, description, avatar, and contact methods. - Designed UI with custom styles and shadow effects for a modern look. - Included support for dynamic loading of contact icons and fallback text. - Added event handling for contact method clicks to emit corresponding signals.
* refactor: 清理 ContactCardWidget 代码，优化格式和注释
* Remove the todo list from the documentation as it is no longer relevant.
* Refactor code structure for improved readability and maintainability
* add(README.MD) add third-party use of icon (Google icon)
* Refactor UI components and improve code structure
- Updated include paths for TcpMgr and httpmgr to reflect new directory structure. - Enhanced MainWindow and LoginDialog with improved comments and code clarity. - Added TimeHelper utility class for performance measurement. - Translated comments and messages to improve readability and maintainability. - Fixed various minor issues in registration and reset dialogs, including validation messages and HTTP request handling.
* 清理未使用的头文件，优化代码结构
* Refactor UI components and improve code comments for clarity
- Updated comments in CustomChatWindow, FaceDetectWindow, MainWindow, and other UI files to provide clearer explanations of the code functionality. - Translated comments from Chinese to English for better accessibility and understanding. - Improved variable naming and code structure in various files to enhance readability and maintainability. - Fixed minor issues in the login and registration dialogs, ensuring proper error messages and user feedback. - Ensured consistent use of coding standards across the project.
* Change the code format to fix the issue of Chinese input in the log module
* 清理未使用的代码，优化项目结构
* 添加头像管理器的头文件和实现文件，支持加载和管理用户头像
* 清理未使用的代码和头文件，优化项目结构
* 添加Qt多线程、互斥、原子和缓存模块的头文件，增强项目的并发处理能力
* Add new avatar images and enhance AvatarManager functionality
- Added multiple avatar images to the Circle header directory. - Introduced a Python script for batch renaming images with random English names. - Enhanced AvatarManager with improved asynchronous loading, caching, and preloading strategies. - Updated logging mechanisms for better tracking of avatar loading processes. - Refactored code for clarity and maintainability, including detailed comments and documentation.
* 删除未使用的头像数据文件和优化AvatarManager实现
